articles.title: Teva and Alvotech launch ustekinumab biosimilar injection in US
articles.summary: Teva Pharmaceuticals and Alvotech have launched Selarsdi (ustekinumab-aekn) injection, a biosimilar to Johnson & Johnsonâ€™s Stelara, in the US. This marks the second biosimilar launched under their strategic collaboration, indicated for various immune-mediated and inflammatory conditions. Selarsdi has received FDA approval in four presentations and is provisionally deemed interchangeable with Stelara from April 30, 2025.
